Spraying Gun (HVLP = High Volume Low Pressure)

http://www.devilbiss.com/products/spray-guns/automatic-spray-guns/hvlp
1. Compact Automatic I HVLP Spray Gun  (656 gms)
2. Compact Automatic X HVLP Spray Gun  (950 gms)
3. Automatic HVLP Spray Gun (840 gr)
Price ~ $1000 (http://www.ccisinc.com/ccis-major-brands/devilbiss-finishing-equipment/devilbiss-automatic-guns/devilbiss-agxv-hvlp-automatic-series)

Industrial robots use brushless motors: either AC servomotors, or brushless DC motors. Cheap. And long life. But controllers are complex and expensive.










